==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sprightliness
<hw>Spright"li*ness</hw> <pr>(-l⟦icr⟧*n⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The quality or state of being sprightly; liveliness; life;
briskness; vigor; activity; gayety; vivacity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In dreams, observe with what a <qex>sprightliness</qex> and
alacrity does she [the soul] exert herself!</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sprightly</ent>⟦br⟧
